249
00:19:01,208 --> 00:19:03,791
Ready? Fence!

250
00:19:07,208 --> 00:19:09,083
Ready? Fence!

251
00:19:23,041 --> 00:19:25,333
Look, Sergey, she will injure her
at this rate.

252
00:19:26,125 --> 00:19:28,083
